{"tid":786334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網傳中國人禁止進入NASA但蔡英文買票就可以參觀及進入控制室？","createTime":"2018-08-20T00:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T03:34:59.000Z","uid":35790,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9b6fa3fa6e179861dd06efb8f7177618f71a1ddf","tid":786334,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:13:32.000Z","msg":"&lt;轉貼&gt;<br />\n對中國人來說是有禁令的，除了擁有綠卡的中國人，中國人禁止進入NASA相關設施，但是只可以進入NASA遊客中心。<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chinese_exclusion_policy_of_NASA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FChinese_exclusion_policy_of_NASA&d=%2BmEGqCqhMWI0lOc0EbPP9dibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=3b974155\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chinese_exclusion_policy_of_NASA</a><br />\n規定在這裡<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1534698743.A.602.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1534698743.A.602.html&d=%2BmEGqCqhMWI0lOc0EbPP9dibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=f10a2ba1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1534698743.A.602.html</a><br />\n中國人不能參觀NASA<br />\n未經證實是否真的？"},{"pid":"a32f1ec1ed1d7506e8366314645ee769af1ee82e","tid":786334,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:14:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a91c1ccc066ae1b80148400144572e61b5028ed","tid":786334,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:16:19.000Z","msg":"推 proprome: <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/uBrcrWP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FuBrcrWP.jpg&h=90d7dc6c&s={SIZE}\" />112.104.98.193 08/20 01:39<br />\n&rarr; proprome: 買票最多只能進到這 112.104.98.193 08/20 01:39"},{"pid":"bd2c7221b2266dcbbb06808f1f1bfdde54d21f22","tid":786334,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:23:14.000Z","msg":"NASA会议禁止中国人参加引起公愤<br />\n<br />\n2013-10-07 08:17 南方都市报<br />\n<a href=\"https://3g.163.com/tech/article/9AIOPLU6000915BF.html#adaptation=pc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F3g.163.com%2Ftech%2Farticle%2F9AIOPLU6000915BF.html%23adaptation%3Dpc&d=%2BmEGqCqhMWI0lOc0EbPP9dibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=65c80b50\" target=\"_blank\">https://3g.163.com/tech/article/9AIOPLU6000915BF.html#adaptation=pc</a>"},{"pid":"4e7f168875ab66740e6358a5542edeeb5391aa28","tid":786334,"uid":12021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:24:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33e3b1a7b3a51be4fc6a3df759ae2ba28093e745","tid":786334,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e7f168875ab66740e6358a5542edeeb5391aa28","tid":786334,"uid":12021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:24:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:32:54.000Z","msg":"用鳳眼與毛蟹滲透敵人"},{"pid":"d227f2256c87840f15819ea905fa1319d310f34f","tid":786334,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:34:56.000Z","msg":"小英唔係中國人？"},{"pid":"0ad2e682ea081a5bdaa625186828feadd7745486","tid":786334,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d227f2256c87840f15819ea905fa1319d310f34f","tid":786334,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:34:56.000Z","msg":"小英唔係中國人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:38:02.000Z","msg":"環時提醒大家台灣人唔係中国人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1675188f641377444046222599116e26b38e22b2","tid":786334,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:38:04.000Z","msg":"台灣總統首次拜訪美官方機構就選在NASA <br />\n環球時報：只要買票，人人都可去<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.thenewslens.com/amparticle/102269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Famparticle%2F102269&d=%2BmEGqCqhMWI0lOc0EbPP9dibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=fe5e8982\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.thenewslens.com/amparticle/102269</a>"},{"pid":"883dac6a1ecffbcfbd61e7f4d8b0d3ad2c69e951","tid":786334,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:15:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33070a9d6c7c3798f55fb2defe49f47e6e1dcff9","tid":786334,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:34:59.000Z","msg":"買票就可進入NASA？鄉民打臉：只要是中國人就進不去<br />\n<br />\n2018-08-20 09:28<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<br />\n總統蔡英文昨（19日）過境美國休士頓時參訪NASA詹森太空中心，成為首位參訪該機構的台灣總統。中國官媒《環球時報》對此氣得跳腳，直說只要買票就可以進入NASA參觀，但這個說法被PTT鄉民搬出相關法條打臉，原來NASA有所謂的「中國人禁令」，除非有綠卡，否則只要是中國人就無法入內，最多只能在遊客中心（visitor Center）逛一逛。<br />\n<br />\n「中國人禁令」於2011年4月由美國國會訂立，禁止美國國家航空暨太空總署使用資金在NASA設施裡接待中國遊客，而且NASA所有研究人員都禁止與中國國企或中國公民進行雙邊合作，以上禁令全是出於安全考量。<br />\n<br />\n鄉民們又指出，就算外國遊客能夠買票進入，最多可能只能在詹森太空中心主控室外參觀，而無法進到裡面與研究人員接觸，但總統蔡英文不僅進入了主控室，還由太空人Michael Fincke全程陪同導覽。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，就連中國人自己也知道所謂的「中國人禁令」，對岸問答網站「知乎」去年有人提問該如何進入NASA工作時，1位匿名用戶坦言，不一定要是美國公民，但一定要有綠卡，因為NASA的中國人禁令是客觀事實，中國留學生和訪問學者若沒有綠卡，一律禁止入內，想要參觀都不行。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"}]}